  "datePublished": "2023-09-03",
  "description": "Fundraising for Onion \u0026amp; Saffron Bulbs, Fall 2023 Hey folks, I know it\u0026rsquo;s been a long while since I\u0026rsquo;ve posted anything anywhere - in fact, it\u0026rsquo;s coming up on about a year since I got kicked of Twitter, which is really probably the last time I was consistent about sharing updates with the Web.\nThe shortest way I can think of to explain what\u0026rsquo;s been going on in my life is that I\u0026rsquo;ve been spending a lot of time being dragged by material needs to recenter the feelings of white dudes over anything I actually care about. This has led to a lot of issues in the lives of me and my comrades, from needing to waste our spiritual energy on nonsense most days of the week, to living among vermin who are encouraged more by others\u0026rsquo; apathy than we\u0026rsquo;re able to resist. There\u0026rsquo;s some decisions and changes happening in the community that support me that\u0026rsquo;ll work to prevent that happening again; one change is that I\u0026rsquo;m going to come back to representing myself, as myself, not focusing on building up a presence for any of the groups I coordinate with.\n",
